query:
SELECT id as "id!: String", 
name as "name!: Option < String >", 
status as "status!: AccountStatus", 
addr as "addr!: Option < String >", 
created_at as "created_at!: UtcDateTime", 
updated_at as "updated_at!: Option < UtcDateTime >", 
claim_signature as "claim_signature!: Option < String >", 
claim_session_id as "claim_session_id!: Option < String >", 
processed_for_legacy_claim as "processed_for_legacy_claim!: bool", 
allows_gasless as "allows_gasless!: bool", 
stripe_customer_id as "stripe_customer_id!: Option < String >", 
unclaimed_asami_balance as "unclaimed_asami_balance!: String", 
unclaimed_doc_balance as "unclaimed_doc_balance!: String", 
asami_balance as "asami_balance!: String", 
doc_balance as "doc_balance!: String", 
rbtc_balance as "rbtc_balance!: String", 
last_on_chain_sync as "last_on_chain_sync!: UtcDateTime", 
force_hydrate as "force_hydrate!: bool", 
total_collabs as "total_collabs!: i32", 
total_collab_rewards as "total_collab_rewards!: String", 
total_campaigns as "total_campaigns!: i32", 
total_collabs_received as "total_collabs_received!: i32", 
total_spent as "total_spent!: String" FROM accounts WHERE (NOT $1::boolean OR id = $2::varchar) AND (NOT $3::boolean OR id = ANY(CAST($4 as varchar[])) ) AND (NOT $5::boolean OR name = $6::varchar) AND (NOT $7::boolean OR name LIKE $8::varchar) AND (NOT $9::boolean OR status = $10::account_status) AND (NOT $11::boolean OR status = ANY(CAST($12 as account_status[])) ) AND (NOT $13::boolean OR addr = $14::varchar) AND (NOT $15::boolean OR addr LIKE $16::varchar) AND ($17::boolean IS NULL OR (($17::boolean AND addr IS NOT NULL) OR (NOT $17::boolean AND addr IS NULL))) AND (NOT $18::boolean OR created_at = $19::timestamptz) AND (NOT $20::boolean OR updated_at = $21::timestamptz) AND (NOT $22::boolean OR claim_signature = $23::varchar) AND (NOT $24::boolean OR claim_session_id = $25::varchar) AND (NOT $26::boolean OR processed_for_legacy_claim = $27::boolean) AND (NOT $28::boolean OR allows_gasless = $29::boolean) AND (NOT $30::boolean OR stripe_customer_id = $31::varchar) AND (NOT $32::boolean OR unclaimed_asami_balance = $33::varchar) AND (NOT $34::boolean OR unclaimed_doc_balance = $35::varchar) AND (NOT $36::boolean OR asami_balance = $37::varchar) AND (NOT $38::boolean OR doc_balance = $39::varchar) AND (NOT $40::boolean OR rbtc_balance = $41::varchar) AND (NOT $42::boolean OR last_on_chain_sync = $43::timestamptz) AND (NOT $44::boolean OR last_on_chain_sync < $45::timestamptz) AND (NOT $46::boolean OR force_hydrate = $47::boolean) AND (NOT $48::boolean OR total_collabs = $49::int4) AND (NOT $50::boolean OR total_collab_rewards = $51::varchar) AND (NOT $52::boolean OR total_campaigns = $53::int4) AND (NOT $54::boolean OR total_collabs_received = $55::int4) AND (NOT $56::boolean OR total_spent = $57::varchar) ORDER BY 
      (CASE ($58 = 'Id' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN id ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'Id' AND $59) WHEN true THEN id ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'Name' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN name ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'Name' AND $59) WHEN true THEN name ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'Status' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN status ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'Status' AND $59) WHEN true THEN status ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'Addr' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN addr ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'Addr' AND $59) WHEN true THEN addr ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'CreatedAt' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN created_at ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'CreatedAt' AND $59) WHEN true THEN created_at ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'UpdatedAt' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN updated_at ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'UpdatedAt' AND $59) WHEN true THEN updated_at ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'ClaimSignature' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN claim_signature ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'ClaimSignature' AND $59) WHEN true THEN claim_signature ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'ClaimSessionId' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN claim_session_id ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'ClaimSessionId' AND $59) WHEN true THEN claim_session_id ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'ProcessedForLegacyClaim' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN processed_for_legacy_claim ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'ProcessedForLegacyClaim' AND $59) WHEN true THEN processed_for_legacy_claim ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'AllowsGasless' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN allows_gasless ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'AllowsGasless' AND $59) WHEN true THEN allows_gasless ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'StripeCustomerId' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN stripe_customer_id ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'StripeCustomerId' AND $59) WHEN true THEN stripe_customer_id ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'UnclaimedAsamiBalance' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN unclaimed_asami_balance ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'UnclaimedAsamiBalance' AND $59) WHEN true THEN unclaimed_asami_balance ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'UnclaimedDocBalance' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN unclaimed_doc_balance ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'UnclaimedDocBalance' AND $59) WHEN true THEN unclaimed_doc_balance ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'AsamiBalance' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN asami_balance ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'AsamiBalance' AND $59) WHEN true THEN asami_balance ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'DocBalance' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN doc_balance ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'DocBalance' AND $59) WHEN true THEN doc_balance ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'RbtcBalance' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN rbtc_balance ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'RbtcBalance' AND $59) WHEN true THEN rbtc_balance ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'LastOnChainSync' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN last_on_chain_sync ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'LastOnChainSync' AND $59) WHEN true THEN last_on_chain_sync ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'ForceHydrate' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN force_hydrate ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'ForceHydrate' AND $59) WHEN true THEN force_hydrate ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'TotalCollabs' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN total_collabs ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'TotalCollabs' AND $59) WHEN true THEN total_collabs ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'TotalCollabRewards' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN total_collab_rewards ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'TotalCollabRewards' AND $59) WHEN true THEN total_collab_rewards ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'TotalCampaigns' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN total_campaigns ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'TotalCampaigns' AND $59) WHEN true THEN total_campaigns ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'TotalCollabsReceived' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN total_collabs_received ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'TotalCollabsReceived' AND $59) WHEN true THEN total_collabs_received ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($58 = 'TotalSpent' AND NOT $59) WHEN true THEN total_spent ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($58 = 'TotalSpent' AND $59) WHEN true THEN total_spent ELSE NULL END) DESC
     LIMIT $60 OFFSET $61 FOR UPDATE
